snippet.textDisplay:
"Mondays"? I won't go any further of fears of accused of speaking for others, but not being in my place to.

It's been EXACTLY a decade since I've seen Avatar & wore shaded glasses when seeing it in 3D. People are still going on about that reference? When you say it's just not me to fight back or be confrontational, I don't think you dumbasses remember or did not register, when I had fights with family members (one in 2012 that resulted me having a case. A blessing in disguise?) or when I physically wrecked things. Not counting me being confrontational with people, sure, something that you didn't see me do since 2014. I was laying low. Maybe people are imagining me being meekish & saying sorry, all the while I shattered each glass panel of our neighbor in Hamilton's greenhouse.
